    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 997.1 Carrera S, a pinnacle of analog engagement. This example features the 3.8L M97 flat-six mated to a precise 6-speed G97 manual transaxle. The mechanical condition is peerless; the IMS bearing has been addressed, and a recent scope confirms zero bore scoring. Equipped with PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) for adaptive damping, the chassis delivers surgical feedback with no bushing deflection. The exterior retains its factory depth, while the interior shows negligible bolster wear. A turn-key, naturally aspirated icon with a documented service history and zero deferred maintenance.",
